        {
            "title": "跨大西洋關係緊張 歐洲抵制美國世界杯的呼聲日漸高漲",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"Photographer: Stuart Franklin/Getty Images\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/JU0CZSDZ30vmdGRCkbVxcA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/53cd9ffc476597d7645c71fc49df2874\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">Photographer: Stuart Franklin/Getty Images</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 美國總統唐納德·川普與歐洲的關係日益緊張，要求考慮抵制今年夏季在該國舉辦的世界杯呼聲也愈發高漲。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">身陷爭議的國際足聯前主席塞普·布拉特周一在社交媒體上發帖，建議球迷「遠離」美國和世界杯。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">此外， 德甲聖保利足球俱樂部主席兼德國足協副主席Oke Göttlich接受《漢堡晨報》採訪時表示，是時候「認真考慮和討論」抵制了。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">國際足聯發言人拒絕置評。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">本屆世界杯將由美國與加拿大和墨西哥聯合舉辦，從6月開始並持續約五周。該賽事過高的票價已經招致批評。現在川普的政策，包括追求吞併格陵蘭引發了關於抵制參賽的辯論。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-a34fc857-ef58-3938-b7e5-da9751d6d93b-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「上世紀80年代抵制奧運會的理由是什麼？」 Göttlich在採訪中提到了前蘇聯入侵阿富汗後不少國家拒絕參加莫斯科奧運會的歷史。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"德甲俱樂部聖保利主席兼德國足協副主席奧克·格特利希希望考慮抵制世界杯。攝影師：Stuart Franklin/Getty Images\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/3DxsPJGdP8DWZIxUm3RG4Q--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/76909bc4dcf85674bbff4ee32ce8753d\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">德甲俱樂部聖保利主席兼德國足協副主席奧克·格特利希希望考慮抵制世界杯。攝影師：Stuart Franklin/Getty Images</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「依我看，現在的潛在威脅比那時候還要大，」 他說，「我們需要就此進行討論。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">英國一些政客和過去十年領導一個委員會負責國際足聯改革的Mark Pieth也持同樣的看法。他表示，美國威權主義愈演愈烈，球迷應該抵制在該國舉辦的世界杯。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Calls for World Cup Boycott Increase After US-Europe Tensions</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%B7%A8%E5%A4%A7%E8%A5%BF%E6%B4%8B%E9%97%9C%E4%BF%82%E7%B7%8A%E5%BC%B5-%E6%AD%90%E6%B4%B2%E6%8A%B5%E5%88%B6%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E6%9D%AF%E7%9A%84%E5%91%BC%E8%81%B2%E6%97%A5%E6%BC%B8%E9%AB%98%E6%BC%B2-193505556.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-27 06:14:42",
